                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9001" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2265</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1039 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“传统控制”到“数字赋能”：纽绅教育的集团管控之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Traditional Control&quot; to &quot;Digital Empowerment&quot;: The Road of Group Control in New Century Education</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈慧，孙孝龙，王佳瑞，丰超，陈怿，向泓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州纽绅教育发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民办教育；集团化；集团管控；权责体系；数字赋能</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Private education; Grouping; Group control; Power and responsibility system; Digital empowerment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着社会发展和国家政策的变化，民办教育行业经历了兴盛、偏航到规范的三个阶段，纽绅集团凭借其高效的管控措施，在时代浪潮中脱颖而出，逐步成长为贵州地区乃至全国极具影响力的综合教育集团。本案例重点描述纽绅集团创立至今的集团管控之路，主要包括三个部分：第一，纽绅集团创办教育的初心及从单一培训学校到创立集团实现集团化办学的发家过程；第二，纽绅集团创立初期如何以权责体系建设为核心，通过多种管控措施解决集团所遇到的管控问题；第三，纽绅集团在发展新时期面对集团财务问题，如何利用数字技术赋能加强集团管控，并以此为契机推动集团整体数字化管控建设。本案例希望通过对纽绅集团从集团创立初期到高质量发展新时期两个阶段管控实践的分析和讨论，引导学生了解、思考和掌握民办教育企业的管控问题成因、集团管控措施和数字化赋能集团管控的相关探索，并为民办教育行业其他企业集团化、集团管控建设提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of society and changes in national policies, the private education industry has gone through three stages of prosperity, yawning to standardization, and New Century Group, with its efficient control measures, has stood out from the tide of the times and gradually grown into a highly influential comprehensive education group in Guizhou and even across the country. This case focuses on describing the road of group control of New Century Group since its establishment, which mainly includes three parts: Firstly, New Century Group&#39;s original intention of founding education and the process of starting a single training school to creating a group to realize the group&#39;s schooling process; Secondly, how to take the construction of the authority and responsibility system as the core in the early stage of founding of New Century Group to solve the group&#39;s encountered control problems through a variety of control measures; Lastly, in the face of the group&#39;s financial problems, how to use digital technology to strengthen the group&#39;s control, and as an opportunity to promote the group&#39;s overall digital control construction. This case hopes that through the analysis and discussion of the control practice of New Century Group from the early stage of the group&#39;s establishment to the new period of high-quality development, to guide the students to understand, think and master the causes of the control problems of the private education enterprises, the group&#39;s control measures and the exploration of the digital empowerment of the group&#39;s control and to provide reference for the construction of the grouping and the group&#39;s control for the other enterprises in the private education industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《集团管控》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">集团化理论；集团权责体系；集团管控；数字赋能</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
